               <msContents class="#CM">
                  <summary><p>A composite manuscript in the form of a bound codex, containing:
<list rend="numbered">
<item>The copy of a Christian catechism in Tamil originally written on palm-leaves.</item>
  <item>The copy of a bilingual text (Marathi and ,Tamil), possibly an inscription.</item>
  <item>A Grantha syllabary.</item>
</list></p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (April 2019).</p>
<p>Dimensions after Cabaton (1912).</p>
 
</summary>
                  
